metadata.name: SPARQ 02 - INFERNO
metadata.description: SPARQ Cells are the key component for creating a Melted Dudz, the newest addition to the Dudelz collection. Simply use this battery in the MYNT-X machine to initiate the process and bring your Dudelz to a whole new level. SPARQ Cells will be destroyed during the process, but your Dudelz NFT will be safe and remain unaltered.
